>
  <p>
    A sewage backup means wastewater has nowhere to go and is coming back toward the house. The
    good news is that your first moves are straightforward, and doing them calmly protects both
    your home and your health while a provider is on the way.
  </p>

  {/* Intended asset: /images/resources/what-to-do-when-sewage-backs-up-hero.webp — see public/images/resources/README.md */}
  <ResourceImageSlot
