  <h2>Is It an Emergency?</h2>
  <p>
    Treat it as urgent when sewage is entering the home or several drains are backing up at once.
    It is less urgent — though still worth prompt attention — when you are catching an early sign
    such as a single slow drain, occasional gurgling or a faint odor. Either way, acting sooner
    tends to keep the problem smaller. For an active backup,
    <a href="/emergency-septic-service-cookeville-tn/">request emergency septic service</a> or
    <a href="/request-service/">send a service request</a> describing what you are seeing.
  </p>

